צאון -   צאן / tsô'n  tse'ôn / tsone, tseh-one'
=== Etymology ===

From an unused root meaning to migrate; 
=== Noun ===
a collective name for a flock (of sheep or goats); also figuratively (of men): - (small) cattle, flock (+ -s), lamb (+ -s), sheep ([-cote, -fold, -shearer, -herds]).